Hei, kaverit!

408
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:43,000
Hei, miten teillä menee?

409
00:29:43,080 --> 00:29:44,800
Kiva. Jumalauta!

410
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:55,160
Anteeksi, tunnenko sinut?

411
